@startuml license-state-diagram
title DVLD License Lifecycle - State Diagram

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #111827
}

[*] --> Active : Issue License

Active --> Expired : Expire License
Active --> Detained : Detain License
Active --> Replaced : Replace Lost/Damaged License
Active --> Inactive : Deactivate License

Expired --> Renewed : Renew License
Renewed --> Active : Activate Renewed License

Detained --> Released : Release License
Released --> Active : Restore Active Status

Replaced --> Inactive : Deactivate Replaced License
Expired --> Inactive : Deactivate License
Detained --> Inactive : Deactivate License

Inactive --> [*]

note right of Active
Only active licenses should be used for
valid driving privileges, replacement,
international-license checks, and detention.
end note

@enduml
